This chatbot is trained on Tamil language and its trained to answer questions about transportation.
The model predicts the output with 99.6% accuracy.
Further more data can be added in the JSON file to train and predict the output.

For example, You can ask :
1. போக்குவரத்து என்றால் என்ன ?
2. சாலை வழி என்றால் என்ன ?

